description: Ibyuma bityaye, imakasi,inzembe n’ibindi bintu byose bityaye yangwa byajombana, nk’ibirahuri byamenetse; bishobora guteza impanuka yo guko-mereka bikomeye.
title: Ibyuma bityaye, imakasi,inzembe n’ibindi bintu byose bityaye yangwa byajombana, nk’ibirahuri byamenetse; bishobora guteza impanuka yo guko-mereka bikomeye.
content: Ibyuma bityaye, imakasi,inzembe n’ibindi bintu byose bityaye yangwa byajombana, nk’ibirahuri byamenetse; bishobora guteza impanuka yo guko-mereka bikomeye. Ibyo bikoresho byose bigomba gushyirwa aho umwana atagera.
